<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Ludystock!</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 px-16 py-14 text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="rounded-full bg-green-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-500 p-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="h-8 w-8 text-white">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="my-4 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700">Welcome to Ludystock!</h3>
        <p class="w-[230px] text-center font-normal text-gray-600">
          Thank you for joining Ludystock, the best platform to find used toys.
          Your account has been successfully created.
          Feel free to browse our catalog and take advantage of our offers.
          If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to contact us.
          Enjoy discovering and happy shopping on Ludystock!
        </p>
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="inline-block mt-6 rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600">Begin the Ludystock adventure !!!</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
